bib_record.title: N-14(g,pn)C-12 Reaction up to Meson Production Threshold.

free_txt: The total cross section  and  angular distributions in
six energy  intervals  of the N-14(g,pn)C-12 reaction
have been measured by means of the diffusion  chamber
in magnetic field exposed to the bremsstrahlung g-ray
beam with energy up  to  150  MeV.  the  results  are
compared  with  the  predictions  of  the  correlated
pn-pair photon  absorption  model  in  the  range  of
energy over the giant resonance region.
Diffusion chamber.
Statistical errors are given.
Diffusion chamber in magnetic field.
15 % mixture of natural nitrogen with hydrogen at
atmosphere pressure.
Directly measurement of product angular distributions.
